{subhead} Simon the Sorcerer 2{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

All hail Epic Ltd.! They've secured a license to port Simon the Sorcerer 2
to the Amiga. Although they are asking for 500 preorders (credit/debit card:
no money taken until day of release) I'm sure they'll easily make that up.
{p} {p}
To secure your copy of this excellent game, contact Epic Marketing in the UK
- their website is at {link http://www.epicmarketing.ltd.net}http://www.epicmarketing.ltd.net{end}
{p} {p}
Requirements: for '030, 8MB, AGA or graphics card and I'd presume also
CD-ROM, but they don't mention it.
{p} {p}
Release: February 2000.
{p} {p}
Price: £25 for Epic Club card holders{p}
       £30 for non-club members